INSERT INTO `history_detail` VALUES (1,'1950\'s','<p>Our journey started in the 50s, as a young company, we traded various products and manufactured hardware, wigs and other products through partnership with other companies.</p>\r\n',1),(1,'1950\'s','<p>我們的旅程開始於50年代，作為一個年輕的公司，我們通過伙伴公司製造過喉管、假髮等各式產品。</p>\r\n',2),(2,'1960\'s','<p>Following this, we manufactured handbag, fashion, sweater and other products with our own factory through the 60s to early 70s.</p>\r\n',1),(2,'1960\'s','<p>到60年代及70年代初，我們開始製造來自自家工廠的手袋、 時裝及毛衫等各式產品。</p>\r\n',2),(3,'1970\'s','<p>The 70s saw one of our businesses, garment manufacturing started to take shape where we manufactured our garments in Hong Kong then gradually expanded into Thailand, Vietnam and China over the years. We became the pioneer in exporting EN standard workwear to Europe.</p>\r\n',1),(3,'1970\'s','<p>上世紀70年代見証了我們製造業務的新一頁，服裝製造開始初具規模，我們的工廠從香港逐步擴展到泰國，越南和中國。我們也成為EN標準工作服出口到歐洲的先驅。</p>\r\n',2),(4,'1980\'s','<p>Between the 70s and the 80s, we added watch band manufacturing into our businesses, where we started to specialize in OEM stainless steel, titanium, solid and wrap type metal watch band and buckle manufacturing for the Top 3 watch makers in Japan.</p>\r\n',1),(4,'1980\'s','<p>70年代末和80年代期間，錶帶製造成我們的業務之一，我們開始專注於OEM不銹鋼、鈦金屬實芯和包片類型手錶錶鍊和錶扣製造, 日本的前三大鐘錶製造商也在我們的客户之列。</p>\r\n',2),(5,'1990\'s','<p>Starting in the 90s, we expanded into food and feed additives (USA FDA registration starting 2005) and chemicals which are exported to Europe, USA and Asia. In 1998, we became the first manufacturer in China to produce EN 345 (EN ISO 20345:2011) standard safety shoes exporting to Europe. The following year, in 1999, Our watch band factory obtained ISO 9001:2000 management system certification.</p>\r\n',1),(5,'1990\'s','<p>在90年代開端，我們再把業務擴展到食品和飼料添加劑 (2005年開始在美國FDA註冊) 和化工品並出口到歐洲、美國和亞洲等國家。在1998, 我們成為了中國第一家生產EN 345（EN ISO 20345：2011）標準安全鞋出口到歐洲的製造商。我們的手錶錶鍊廠也於1999獲得了ISO 9001：2000管理體系認證。</p>\r\n',2),(6,'2010\'s','<p>In 2013, we opened a new manufacturing and trading hub in Cambodia. As of today, our products also include outdoor furniture, gloves and other products.</p>\r\n',1),(6,'2010\'s','<p>到了2013, 我們更在柬埔寨加增了工廠及貿易樞紐。時到今日, 我們的產品還包括戶外傢俱、手套等產品。</p>\r\n',2);
